reviewText: What's not to love?  Denis Leary is always a lot of fun to watch a standup for.  He is always great and this DVD is no exception.
Title: Denis Leary - The Ultimate Collection

reviewText: If you're the type of person who's really into nasty jokes and likes the "f" word a lot, I recommend this movie to rent only (not buy).
Title: Denis Leary - The Ultimate Collection

reviewText: This DVD is a must have for all Denis Leary fans. Don't even hesitate. Buy it, and be totally entertained by the "King of Great Comedy.
Title: Denis Leary - The Ultimate Collection

reviewText: Denis Leary is a hilarious stand-up comedian. Why is it that all the great stand-ups get more famous and then stop doing what they were best at??? Eddie Murphy, this means you...among others.
Title: Denis Leary - The Ultimate Collection

reviewText: Read the reviews before I bought this Gem, and could not believe that people not knowing seeing Denis Leary's stand up is not going to church and if you cant handle great comedy then this is not for you, don't think i stopped laughing though all of it and the extra behind the seen is priceless. If you have a sense of humor this is a must have. He is what comedy is all about. From his classic A**Hole song to the early years left me wanting more.
Title: Denis Leary - The Ultimate Collection
